title: S15 Ep71: Superhuman: The Invisible Made Visible
itunes:title: Superhuman: The Invisible Made Visible
description:
Darkness Radio watches the Superhuman: The Invisible made Visible with guest Caroline Corey

Today we discuss THE MOST POWERFUL documentary Dave has ever seen.

Superhuman is based on the jaw-dropping experiences of individuals with extra-sensory powers that seem to defy the laws of physics known to man today. Producer and Host Caroline Cory takes the viewers on an extraordinary journey to achieve tangible and measurable proof of these seemingly miraculous phenomena.

Watch the documentary here: https://www.superhumanfilm.com/
